divs: Sighting DetailsI has out front in my garage and I was looking at the moon and notice air planes and police helicopter at a distance and at the same time I notice this light moving thats not flashing like air planes and helicopter do.Its was bright and moving fast till the light vanish.The air planes and helicopter I could still track them an see them.The light just vanish.
